  "rationale": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is correct. The equation of a circle in the <em>x</em><em>y</em>-plane can be written as <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus h right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus k right parenthesis squared equals r squared\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>h</mi><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>k</mi><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, where the center of the circle is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis h comma k right parenthesis\"><mo>(</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>)</mo></math> and the radius of the circle is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi></math>. It's given that the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>. This equation&nbsp;can be written as <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus left parenthesis negative 7 right parenthesis right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>)</mo><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>. For this equation, it follows that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"h equals 1\"><mi>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k equals negative 7\"><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn></math>. Therefore, the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane defined by the given equation is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis 1 comma negative 7 right parenthesis\"><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>)</mo></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is incorrect. This is the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane that is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x plus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect. This is the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane that is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x plus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect. This is the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane that is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p>",
